def my_func(input1: str, input2: str):
    if len(input1) < 1 or len(input1) > 20 or len(input2) < 1 or len(input2) > 20:
        return []
    indices = []
    start = 0
    while True:
        start = input1.find(input2, start)
        if start == -1:
            break
        indices.append(start)
        start += 1
    return indices
